Pinkie Pie?

267
00:11:27,210 --> 00:11:29,420
Hmm?
Well, I think...

268
00:11:29,770 --> 00:11:30,560
you're jealous.

269
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,450
Jealous?!

270
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:32,610
