284
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:04,400
Maybe Gilda isn't a big, mean,
grumpy, mean, meany pants.

285
00:12:04,680 --> 00:12:07,020
Maybe I'm just a big, jealous,
judgmental,

286
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:08,830
Jealous, jealousy pants.

287
00:12:09,550 --> 00:12:10,490
[ Sighs ]

288
00:12:12,250 --> 00:12:14,340
[ Slurping ]

289
00:12:15,180 --> 00:12:16,650
