294
00:12:24,870 --> 00:12:27,450
That's cool, I guess.
I'm gonna go chow down!

295
00:12:27,570 --> 00:12:28,540
Later!

296
00:12:32,880 --> 00:12:34,170
[ Sniffs ]

297
00:12:34,220 --> 00:12:37,300
Aah! A rattler!
A rattler!

298
00:12:37,370 --> 00:12:38,330
Run for the hills!

299
00:12:38,460 --> 00:12:41,020
Everybody, run!
Save yourselves!

300
00:12:45,340 --> 00:12:47,330
This stuff
ain't fresh, dude.

301
00:12:47,690 --> 00:12:49,400
Aw, poor Granny Smith!

302
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:50,890
She didn't know
it was a joke!

303
00:12:51,010 --> 00:12:52,070
How mean!

304
00:12:52,510 --> 00:12:54,560
No, no.
I can't misjudge her.

305
00:12:54,940 --> 00:12:56,860
It was kind of a funny prank,
I guess.

306
00:13:00,530 --> 00:13:01,540
